    "uen": "201833937C",
    "description": "<p>Mount Pleasant Veterinary Group has been providing exceptional and compassionate vet care for our animal companions and the community in Singapore for over 30 years. We operate 7 islandwide clinics, including a 24-hour tertiary care centre for patients requiring intensive and critical care.<br>\n<br>\nOur team consists of referral clinicians, senior vets with memberships in small animal internal medicine and <a href=\"http://www.mountpleasant.com.sg/gelenggang/\">surgery</a>, as well as vets with various special interests including avian medicine, dermatology, <a href=\"https://www.mountpleasant.com.sg/clementi/\">ophthalmology</a>, surgery and veterinary acupuncture.<br>\n<br>\nWe launched our <a href=\"http://www.mountpleasant.com.sg/news/clinic-programmes/mount-pleasant-blood-donor-programme/\">Mount Pleasant Blood Donor Programme</a> in 2016 to save more lives.<br>\n<br>\nOn 31 March 2021, Mount Pleasant Veterinary Group joined the <a href=\"http://www.marsveterinary.com/\">Mars Veterinary Health</a> family which includes approximately 70,000+ veterinary professionals globally.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WHY JOIN US?</strong></p>\n<p>At Moun Pleasant Veterinary Group (MPVG), we aim to provide progressive and comprehensive care through the practice of evidence-based medicine. We believe that excellence in client and patient care is achieved by investing in continuing education for our associates and in providing the most advance veterinary technology.</p>\n<p>We invite you to join our team, to share our love for animals!</p>",
